      • fixInaccuraciesTBA

        public boolean fixInaccuraciesTBA()
        Fixes errors made in scouting entries based on match details from The Blue Alliance For the 2019 season, this fixes HAB line crossings, starting levels, partner climbs assisted, and HAB climbs Generates a list of inaccuracies, along with scout names, team numbers and match numbers
        Returns:
        true if inaccuracies are found, false otherwise or if the score breakdown data file does not exist or cannot be downloaded
